  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of our agents has had her cover blown, her job was to intervene in the creation of a new biological weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your job is to retrieve the agent and destroy anything and everything related to the research.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your codename for this operation will be Delta 1.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are now in charge of the operation, you will bring your own equipment, anything else must be acquired on site.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember, no survivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >======================================</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/1598bf46f02e9705228531649373d648.poster.avif?t=1756497470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/1598bf46f02e9705228531649373d648.webm?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/1598bf46f02e9705228531649373d648.mp4?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal is simply to reach the main elevator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill as many zombies as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve small puzzles to progress through the scenario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect capybara trophies scattered in hidden places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save your rifle for large groups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out of ammo? Use your secondary weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kick the zombies if they get too close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid the facility armed security system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for hidden supplies that will help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/53a9e4fa3aa7ce8ec31f087f7044cc52.poster.avif?t=1756497470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/53a9e4fa3aa7ce8ec31f087f7044cc52.webm?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/53a9e4fa3aa7ce8ec31f087f7044cc52.mp4?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of our agents has had her cover blown, her job was to intervene in the creation of a new biological weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your job is to retrieve the agent and destroy anything and everything related to the research.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your codename for this operation will be Delta 1.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are now in charge of the operation, you will bring your own equipment, anything else must be acquired on site.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember, no survivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >======================================</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/1598bf46f02e9705228531649373d648.poster.avif?t=1756497470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/1598bf46f02e9705228531649373d648.webm?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/1598bf46f02e9705228531649373d648.mp4?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal is simply to reach the main elevator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill as many zombies as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve small puzzles to progress through the scenario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect capybara trophies scattered in hidden places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save your rifle for large groups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out of ammo? Use your secondary weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kick the zombies if they get too close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid the facility armed security system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for hidden supplies that will help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/53a9e4fa3aa7ce8ec31f087f7044cc52.poster.avif?t=1756497470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/53a9e4fa3aa7ce8ec31f087f7044cc52.webm?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276450/extras/53a9e4fa3aa7ce8ec31f087f7044cc52.mp4?t=1756497470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
